Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:58.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}ああオレたちには見えてるモノがある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:58.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}啊 有些东西映入我们眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}きっと誰にも奪われないモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}一定没有人能够夺走它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}無意味じゃない　あの意図が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}那并非毫无意义的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那是便利店的垃圾箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正千万别接近平和岛静雄这人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿静的暴力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道理说不通三句谈不拢 不好办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没告诫过你不许再来池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄 打架可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？池袋最强？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说还是那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和岛静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}ああ朝日は昇る 水平線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}啊 旭日初升 越过水平线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.79,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}今　信じれば変わるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}此刻只要相信 就能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:48.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}無意味じゃない　あの光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:48.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}那并非毫无意义的一线光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司突然说要炒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还赶我出宿舍 太突然了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辞退金也不给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙食费 生活费也没影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家还不帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 都怪国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是国家不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是借了钱来风流快活？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷妹妹和我是真心相爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这家店里见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道手机号码
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们是有真爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这家店里见到她？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道手机号码？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先声明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真爱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fn微软雅黑\1c&Hffffff&}{\1c&H0F3DC8&}国{\1c&HFFFFFF&}士无双
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说最近平和岛静雄好像闹得很凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个穿着调酒师服的人吧？平和岛静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他本来就很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近又变本加厉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋现在乱得像战场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我以前也见过他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个很可怕的人呢 平和岛静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不要凭道听途说就下判断比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀塞顿 你认识平和岛静雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…那条道上的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都被你打飞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还怎么收钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是两三天前就没回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这种人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是传闻中狩猎人类那帮家伙干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么有伤员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是砍人魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 往那边逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 池袋又变得多事起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很臭 整座城市臭气熏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 静雄 托姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 塞蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 最近他心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄 青春期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那算叛逆期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印章？（音近）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是电影的主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽岛幽平很活跃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…平和岛幽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当哥哥的很有面子吧 平和岛静雄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 其实我是做这行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅有外表 演技也相当精湛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出道作叫什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 『吸血忍者卡密拉才藏』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我就觉得他将来能成大器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得动作戏也不用替身就出色完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有哥哥的指导呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天关于这个话题 请您务必谈几句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我一开始也不是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是和弟弟幽吵架的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因一些鸡毛蒜皮的事发火的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬起冰箱想扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的 不许吃\N静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我想搬它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是不得不搬它而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我控制不住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火气上来身体便不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后每次都会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有所谓火灾现场的蛮力（狗急跳墙）嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄同学肯定能整天使用这种力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑会抑制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为一旦超越极限 骨头和肌肉就会受损
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是静雄同学的大脑却让力量爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可谓是生命的奥秘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人瞠目结舌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你的身体让我检…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了 疼死了啊 静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体细节我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}断了 要断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是遏制不住怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}尺骨 尺骨 我的尺骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后破坏周围的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的身体也随之损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只明白这点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃了忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然做不到那一开始就没必要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会搞坏身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体伤过许多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而每次都让我变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按新罗的说法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是在不断变强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是会受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 要多喝牛奶长壮点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闯祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 回过神来 我就已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家是个普通的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么心理阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我刚进来良的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开张纪念 优惠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到又能上同一所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是命中注定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后身体情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 为了庆祝我们重逢替你检查…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么至少抽点血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞尔堤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚不回家担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去找脑袋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上这么说 不是上哪找了个相好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞尔堤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别若无其事地戳人心口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}塞尔堤 我给你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}他是我朋友 叫平和岛静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该怎么表达好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}静雄 塞尔堤是跟我合住的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得这家伙不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}或者说是将来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起烦心事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 那只跳蚤混账也是在那时出现在我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 折原临也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是和我一个初中的折原临也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}唔 其实不算什么好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一眼我就看他不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}不如说相当惹人厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊 新罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 本以为能和你相处愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛 静雄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 很愉快对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面当天 我就和临也打得死去活来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要理由 只是看他不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 他身体结实得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…失策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊 临也也在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你怎么没受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}以后的日子变得无比烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的家伙接连不断地找上门干架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想过安宁日子而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼见鬼见鬼见鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦躁烦躁烦躁烦躁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是临也 是临也在幕后指使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了这点后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临·也！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把他宰了就清静了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来良毕业后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 合身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋从事这活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳蚤和黑道上的人混在一起 不知干什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之暂时平静了一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演员羽岛幽平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小幽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调酒师服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得工作别换太频繁比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能一直干下去 就买了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临·也！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跳蚤混账陷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他离开了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很快被无罪释放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 没能遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs40}（不要饮酒驾驶 和我的约定）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这不静雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆是我初中的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮他回收债务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了就是当保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初我没想接这活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不用你勉强出手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋只要听到平和岛静雄的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没人敢反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那时起小幽也开始变成了大忙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再也没见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平先生 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的 感觉轻松了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是到现在我还跟着托姆干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还款期限？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太复杂我不懂哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是宽松教育嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 学校社会 都是他们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有心理阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了我们不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚吧大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔这也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 瞧这什么打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是管家啦管家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个不知道静雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他谁？名人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗管家先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗 我喷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给本小姐换一杯吗 管家先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋混居然不知道静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是宽松教育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢弄脏我衣服…弟弟送给我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是不喜欢暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强到能遏制住自己的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你说了后感觉一身轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直烦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我听到些传闻 有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你真的很喜欢弟弟啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和别人保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法独来独往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以渴望与别人有所联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托姆 小幽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙肯定也想和他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静雄
