Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来盘寿司？寿司大大的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪觉得臭气熏天 原来是你
